thread.title: Woman wounds three at YouTube headquarters in California before killing herself

title: Woman wounds three at YouTube headquarters in California before killing herself
text:
Woman wounds three at YouTube headquarters in California before killing herself 1:10pm IST - 01:12 
A woman opened fire at YouTube's headquarters near San Francisco on Tuesday, wounding at least three people before taking her own life, as employees of the video website scrambled into the surrounding streets for safety.
